{"tid":1255912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1:民間馬拉松抗爭 趁G20向習施壓","createTime":"2019-06-24T17:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:10:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"705dd1c46c991b9c902766cae8825d149998b431","tid":1255912,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65007469_10157778685562448_6538639107415867392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQl0B2w0V1NFaHavwCLdK8krIITnqFRvh72NLpyesMbcS2k3j2aThCKbNEQR_FiB6Oc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=98c7b022ce0eb70fd491450502df0a91&amp;oe=5D8090FE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65007469_10157778685562448_6538639107415867392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQl0B2w0V1NFaHavwCLdK8krIITnqFRvh72NLpyesMbcS2k3j2aThCKbNEQR_FiB6Oc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D98c7b022ce0eb70fd491450502df0a91%26oe%3D5D8090FE&h=721fc852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【A1頭條】香港八日內兩次過百萬人反送中大遊行，震撼全球，美國早前預告美國總統特朗普將於日本二十國集團(G20)峯會期間，與中國國家主席習近平討論香港議題。本港多個民間組織趁G20峯會舉行在即，在港舉行馬拉松式抗爭，由明日起至本周五舉行集會，並到與會國家駐港領事館請願，希望國際關注香港現況，向習近平施壓，力爭撤回惡法，並盡快推動香港政制改革，全面落實真普選。"},{"pid":"986d6c105a073494c955e6858c7c6905877c0093","tid":1255912,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"連登街站團！<br />\n公海link: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期戰就係要落地開花，令議題喺各地保持熱度，大家幫到既盡幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}